ce soir!<delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Ils te jetteront un sort!<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Et donc<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Un bonbon ou un sort!<delay frames="60" /> <anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Tu peux
