	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Tu m'as offert un bonbon,<delay8 /> alors
en échange,<delay8 /> moi je t'offre
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="2" /><colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" />.</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Tu sais quoi,<delay8 /> moi aussi j'ai des
confiseries pour toi.<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Un <colour id="1" />suçon<colour id="65535" />,<delay8 />
